instruction: twenty names of famous horses and who they belonged to
output:
1. Secretariat - Owned by Meadow Stable
2. Seabiscuit - Owned by Charles Howard
3. Black Caviar - Owned by the Lloyd Williams
4. Red Rum - Owned by Noel Le Mare
5. Phar Lap - Owned by David Davis
6. Trigger - Owned by Roy Rogers
7. Mr. Ed - Owned by Allan Lane
8. Man o' War - Owned by Samuel D. Riddle
9. Citation - Owned by Calumet Farm
10. Affirmed - Owned by Harbor View Farm
11. Kelso - Owned by William Woodward Jr.
12. Zenyatta - Owned by Jerry and Ann Moss
13. American Pharoah - Owned by Ahmed Zayat
14. Whirlaway - Owned by Lawrence B. Ellison
15. War Admiral - Owned by Riddle Stable
16. John Henry - Owned by Sam R. Thompson
17. Forego - Owned by Allen E. Paulson
18. Cigar - Owned by Allen E. Paulson
19. Alydar - Owned by the Calumet Farm
20. Ruffian - Owned by Stuart and Barbara Janney
